{"tid":569203,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"肥施離世，終年60歲 車保羅悲慟：見唔到佢最後一面","createTime":"2018-02-22T13:09:44.000Z","updateTime":"2018-03-07T10:43:06.000Z","uid":22675,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"475f5160a50a19a5e087e2213b22793a98945ac3","tid":569203,"uid":22675,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-22T13:09:44.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/02/22/210940_3da9c873d1f8ae1d4aac529268a3b054.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F02%2F22%2F210940_3da9c873d1f8ae1d4aac529268a3b054.png&h=71e63b6d&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n即時娛樂  2018-02-22 20:42:39 HKT\t <br />\n         <br />\n<br />\n一個身高6呎3，一個體重曾經超過300磅，58歲的車保羅，與比他年長兩歲的施介強（肥施）是一對活孖寶，90年代接戲接到手軟，除咗歷蘇主演嘅《香港也瘋狂》同《危情》等等之外，最令人深刻的當然是《審死官》中的瘦虎肥龍。去年初兩人一齊接受《蘋果》專訪笑談近況，今日突傳來肥施離世的消息。<br />\n<br />\n車保羅今晚近九時接受《蘋果》電話訪問，傷心地謂：「今日收到朋友電話，叫我去伊利沙伯醫院見肥施最後一面，我好突然，唔知佢入咗醫院，我喺博愛做緊嘢去唔到，點知冇幾耐，張文慈就打電話比我，話肥施走咗。」<br />\n<br />\n車保羅續說：「我好遺憾見唔到佢最後一面，好難過，佢係我好兄弟，我收咗線之後都忍唔住喊出嚟。」<br />\n<br />\n張文慈當年同肥施合作亞視劇，她稱：「今日收到電話，話肥施唔得喇，叫大家去醫院見佢最後一面，我同尹天照去到，佢已經昏迷。佢今晚7點59分就走咗，屋企人喺佢身邊，佢好辛苦，屋企人決定同佢拔喉。」<br />\n<br />\n肥施一路有糖尿病，年三十晚入醫院，情況一路好差，今日家人見其情況轉差，即急通知親友往探望。"},{"pid":"1118c7bcd625b74ef986dade700b71726ad15a6d","tid":569203,"uid":26752,"like":11,"dislike":3,"score":8,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-22T13:10:56.000Z","msg":"仲以為係肥絲（大隻）離世<img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"881b325b534004add29d8e517b49d6348c0a45f6","tid":569203,"uid":47359,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-02-22T13:13:18.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">肥絲<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/23.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> </span>"},{"pid":"559f7c72e457e0b735405f97c096b10277c25bfc","tid":569203,"uid":22675,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-22T13:21:57.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e4809a1b2cfb4bd5c32d3f34e2c231db8448f4f2","tid":569203,"uid":22675,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-22T14:54:04.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f23d73659ed4d86d110e4b176ea34d22ad942c76","tid":569203,"uid":55309,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-22T14:56:18.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"cd3022e8f5764ebb4598d945f94c6bca558048f1","tid":569203,"uid":57705,"like":1,"dislike":3,"score":-2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-02-22T14:59:49.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"0619316d5222c3a90021e80d82a1474b61b4e1b1","tid":569203,"uid":47359,"like":2,"dislike":2,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"cd3022e8f5764ebb4598d945f94c6bca558048f1","tid":569203,"uid":57705,"like":1,"dislike":3,"score":-2,"quote":{"pid":"881b325b534004add29d8e517b49d6348c0a45f6","tid":569203,"uid":47359,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-02-22T13:13:18.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">肥絲<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/23.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> </span>"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-02-22T14:59:49.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-02-22T15:03:21.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">五毛D wade<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/02/22/230320_ea3dc39ca0b2f6b5f17abddec1f0e9a4.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F02%2F22%2F230320_ea3dc39ca0b2f6b5f17abddec1f0e9a4.png&h=cc6ac7e7&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n</span>"},{"pid":"5371431a3141ed6f5d48bab436d515180b9d9e19","tid":569203,"uid":57705,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-22T15:09:31.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"0055c79c0989f3858f9c6fb127f1a33720f5ca32","tid":569203,"uid":22675,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-07T09:48:58.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"56e563819daab5c65bacc2878987dc6055c1d743","tid":569203,"uid":67500,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-07T10:43:06.000Z","msg":"都唔識改名，癬疥強"}]}